Exercise.Name: Frontier Lunges
Exercise.Description: Step forward with one leg into a lunge position, keeping your upper body straight. Push back to starting position and repeat with the other leg.

Exercise.Name: Open Plains Push-ups
Exercise.Description: Assume a push-up position with your hands slightly wider than shoulder-width apart. Lower your body down until your chest almost touches the ground, then push back up to the starting position.

Exercise.Name: Treacherous River Plank
Exercise.Description: Get into a plank position with your forearms on the ground and your body in a straight line. Hold this position for the designated time.

Exercise.Name: Harmony Hip Bridges
Exercise.Description: Lie on your back with your knees bent and feet flat on the ground. Lift your hips off the ground until your body forms a straight line from your knees to your shoulders, then lower back down.

Exercise.Name: Love for the Land Bicycle Crunches
Exercise.Description: Lie on your back with your hands behind your head and your knees bent. Bring one elbow to the opposite knee while extending the other leg, then switch sides in a pedaling motion.
